  "detailed_description": "Pixel Puzzles 2: Christmas is a traditional style jigsaw puzzle game, featuring 25 images in a festive style, with each puzzle piece uniquely shaped in a way no physical puzzle could be.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>25 puzzles in a range of sizes from 60 to 350 pieces.<br></li><li>Beautiful Christmas themed images.<br></li><li>Auto saving, never lose your progress.<br></li><li>Peaceful puzzling atmosphere.<br></li><li>Traditional puzzle gameplay.<br></li><li>26 Steam Achievements.<br></li><li>Puzzle piece rotation.<br></li><li>Interactive play environment.</li></ul>",
